'''丹尼尔·帕特里克·沃兹尼亚克'''（{{lang-en|Daniel Patrick Wozniak}}，{{bd|1984年|3月23日}}），加利福尼亚谋杀犯。沃兹尼亚克于2010年5月杀害了他的邻居塞缪尔·埃利泽·赫尔（Samuel Eliezer Herr）和邻居的朋友朱里·基比石（Juri Kibuishi）。 

案发前，沃兹尼亚克负债累累，他和未婚妻蕾切尔·梅·巴菲特（Rachel Mae Buffett）因付不起房租即将被赶出公寓。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Actor decapitated neighbor, performed in musical soon after|url=https://nypost.com/2015/12/17/theater-actor-decapitated-neighbor-performed-in-musical-hours-later/|accessdate=2019-07-06|author=Associated Press|work=nypost.com|publisher=NYP HOLDINGS, INC.|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092642/http://nypost.com/2015/12/17/theater-actor-decapitated-neighbor-performed-in-musical-hours-later/|dead-url=no}}</ref>沃兹尼亚克、巴菲特和赫尔都住在加利福尼亚州[[科斯塔梅薩|科斯塔梅萨]]的同一套公寓里。 

经过五年多的诉讼，沃兹尼亚克因两项一级谋杀罪<ref name="OC Register Dec 15">{{Cite news|author=BERG|first=TOM|title=Justice delayed: Why it took more than 5 years for trial of Daniel Wozniak, accused of killing 2, beheading one victim|url=http://www.ocregister.com/2015/12/07/justice-delayed-why-it-took-more-than-5-years-for-trial-of-daniel-wozniak-accused-of-killing-2-beheading-one-victim/|accessdate=2017-10-16|work=Orange County Register|publisher=Southern California News Group|date=2015-12-07|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123194613/https://www.ocregister.com/2015/12/07/justice-delayed-why-it-took-more-than-5-years-for-trial-of-daniel-wozniak-accused-of-killing-2-beheading-one-victim/|dead-url=no}}</ref>于2016年9月被判处死刑。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Andrews|first=Travis M.|title=Community theater actor sentenced to death for killing, dismembering Afghanistan vet to pay for wedding|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/09/26/community-theater-actor-sentenced-to-death-for-robbing-shooting-and-dismembering-afghanistan-vet-to-pay-for-wedding/|accessdate=2017-10-16|work=Washington Post|date=2016-09-26|archive-date=2018-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916060229/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/09/26/community-theater-actor-sentenced-to-death-for-robbing-shooting-and-dismembering-afghanistan-vet-to-pay-for-wedding/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

沃兹尼亚克目前被关在加利福尼亚[[聖昆丁州立監獄|圣昆汀州立监狱]]。<ref>{{Cite news|author=DALTON|first=REX|title=Local Figures Loom Large in Death Penalty Ballot Measure {{!}} Voice of OC|url=https://voiceofoc.org/2016/10/local-figures-loom-large-in-death-penalty-ballot-measure/|accessdate=2017-10-16|work=voiceofoc.org|publisher=Voice of OC|date=2016-10-31|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105212514/https://voiceofoc.org/2016/10/local-figures-loom-large-in-death-penalty-ballot-measure/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 谋杀 ==
沃兹尼亚克于2010年5月21日在[[洛斯阿拉米托斯_(加利福尼亚州)|洛斯阿拉米托斯]]某剧院开枪打死了邻居塞缪尔·赫尔（26岁）。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Dobruck|first=Jeremiah|title=Father describes horror of his dismembered son's murder|url=https://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-father-horror-dismembered-son-murder-20160104-story.html|accessdate=2017-10-16|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2016-01-04|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105203509/https://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-father-horror-dismembered-son-murder-20160104-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>沃兹尼亚克负债累累，付不起房租，还要为即将到来的的婚礼和蜜月筹钱，想要偷赫尔的钱。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Katz|first=Michele|title=Actor decapitates Army combat vet and kills vet's girlfriend|url=http://popularmilitary.com/actor-kills-army-combat-vet-decapitates-vets-girlfriend/|accessdate=2017-10-16|work=Military News|publisher=Bright Mountain Media, Inc.|date=2015-12-18|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122083933/https://popularmilitary.com/actor-kills-army-combat-vet-decapitates-vets-girlfriend/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

为了误导警方，沃兹尼亚克用赫尔的手机给23岁的Juri Kibuishi发了短信。Kibuishi是赫尔在奥兰治海岸学院时的朋友。他将Kibuishi诱骗到赫尔的公寓并枪杀。随后，沃兹尼亚克伪造了犯罪现场，使警方误认为赫尔性侵Kibuishi后杀人，畏罪潜逃。 

当晚，他继续在当地剧院演出。之后，沃兹尼亚克割下赫尔的四肢和头部将其肢解。 

警方误认为赫尔将Kibuishi杀害，展开了大规模的追捕。 

沃兹尼亚克指示一个十六岁的孩子从赫尔的帐户中提款，于是进入了警方的视线。警察找到男孩问话，男孩告诉警察说沃兹尼亚克要他帮忙取钱。<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nzO4A-tPdTg</ref>沃兹尼亚克在婚礼前两天被逮捕。<ref name="Daniel Wozniak Murders: Killer Had a Larger-Than-Life Personality, Friends Say">{{Cite web|title=Daniel Wozniak Murders: Killer Had a Larger-Than-Life Personality, Friends Say|url=http://people.com/crime/daniel-wozniak-murder-case-a-grooms-deadly-scheme/|author=Christine Pelisek|date=2015-03-13|work=People|accessdate=2020-08-20|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123205145/https://people.com/crime/daniel-wozniak-murder-case-a-grooms-deadly-scheme/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ex-actor Daniel Wozniak sentenced to death in double murder and grisly cover-up">{{Cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/local/orangecounty/tn-dpt-me-wozniak-20160923-story.html|title=Ex-actor Daniel Wozniak sentenced to death in double murder and grisly cover-up|author=Hannah Fry|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2016-09-23|accessdate=2020-08-20|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113200615/https://www.latimes.com/local/orangecounty/tn-dpt-me-wozniak-20160923-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

经过一番抵赖后，沃兹尼亚克最终还是认罪了。他带警察到[[長灘_(加利福尼亞州)|长滩]]El Dorado自然中心挖出赫尔的尸体。经过历时五年多的诉讼后，沃兹尼亚克因两项一级谋杀罪被定罪，2016年9月被判处死刑。 

2012年11月，沃兹尼亚克的未婚妻蕾切尔·梅·巴菲特被捕<ref name="OC Register November 2012">{{Cite news|author=EMERY|first=SEAN|title=Actor's ex-fiancée arrested in killings, dismemberment|url=https://www.ocregister.com/2012/11/22/actors-ex-fiance-arrested-in-killings-dismemberment/|accessdate=2018-02-02|work=Staff|publisher=The Orange County Register|date=2012-11-22|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111205519/https://www.ocregister.com/2012/11/22/actors-ex-fiance-arrested-in-killings-dismemberment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被控犯有三项[[幫助犯|事后从犯]]重罪，多次对警方撒谎。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Coker|first=Matt|title=Brother of Death Row Double Murderer Dan Wozniak Held for Domestic Violence|url=http://www.ocweekly.com/news/brother-of-death-row-double-murderer-dan-wozniak-held-for-domestic-violence-7765445|accessdate=2017-10-16|work=OC Weekly|date=2016-12-23|archive-date=2017-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171017093535/http://www.ocweekly.com/news/brother-of-death-row-double-murderer-dan-wozniak-held-for-domestic-violence-7765445|dead-url=no}}</ref>她于2018年9月12日因其中两项罪名而被定罪，最长可判处44个月徒刑。2018年11月8日，她被判处32个月徒刑。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://people.com/crime/daniel-wozniak-fiancee-convicted-lied-police-double-murder/|title=Ex-Disney Princess Lied to Police Hoping to Help Actor Fiancé Get Away with Double-Murder|work=PEOPLE.com|accessdate=2018-09-16|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106064011/https://people.com/crime/daniel-wozniak-fiancee-convicted-lied-police-double-murder/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ex-fiancée of Orange County killer Wozniak is sentenced as accessory|url=https://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-wozniak-20181109-story.html|accessdate=2019-07-06|author=Sclafani|first=Julia|work=latimes.com|publisher=Los Angeles Times|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094009/https://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-wozniak-20181109-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

